The grille is large and spans the width of the front bumper, covering most of the lower portion of the car's face. It has a horizontal slat design, which is common in many modern car designs, providing both aesthetic appeal and functional air intake.

The Acura emblem is prominently displayed at the center of the grille. It is circular in shape and features a three-dimensional design with a silver background. The emblem includes the iconic Acura logo, which consists of a stylized "A" within a circle, surrounded by a ring. The emblem's size is significant compared to the grille, making it easily noticeable upon first glance. The emblem's metallic sheen contrasts with the matte texture of the grille, further emphasizing its presence.

This combination of a textured grille and a prominent, three-dimensional emblem helps distinguish this Acura model from other sedans in terms of its front-end styling. The overall design is sleek and modern, reflecting the brand's focus on luxury and performance.
